1
00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:16,500
Watak, tingkah laku, tempat, organisasi, pekerjaan dan peristiwa dalam drama ini adalah rekaan semata-mata untuk hiburan. Tiada niat untuk membimbing atau menggalakkan sebarang tingkah laku yang muncul dalam drama. Sila gunakan budi bicara semasa menonton.

2
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:42,120
[Imbasan Episod Lalu]

3
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:18,330
Memandangkan awak dah putus dengan teman lelaki,

4
00:00:18,330 --> 00:00:19,800
apa kata cuba sesuatu yang baharu.

5
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,200
Percayalah, awak boleh.

6
00:00:21,670 --> 00:00:23,870
Ada peluang untuk berbaik semula.

7
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:25,300
Dah bercium pun.

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,000
Awak patutnya okey, kan?

9
00:00:27,770 --> 00:00:29,400
Bukan ke awak kata dia bukan cita rasa awak?

10
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:30,660
Cinta satu malam saja.

11
00:00:31,300 --> 00:00:31,940
Bambi.

12
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:33,330
Awak salah orang.

13
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,530
Kita tak patut bercium malam itu.

14
00:00:35,530 --> 00:00:36,930
Susah untuk jadi adik awak lagi.

15
00:00:36,930 --> 00:00:37,730
Maafkan saya.

16
00:00:37,730 --> 00:00:39,590
Saya tak sangka dia akan kembali.

17
00:00:40,170 --> 00:00:42,630
Awak nak lebih daripada cinta satu malam ke?

18
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,600
Terima kasih banyak-banyak kepada semua

19
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,660
kerana datang menyokong Bambi dan Fiona kami hari ini.

20
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:06,290
Serta pelbagai produksi video syarikat kami.

21
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,940
Semua rasa dia cantik tak?

22
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:09,020
Cantik. Sangat cantik.

23
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,620
- Sempurna! - Cantik sangat!

24
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:12,780
- Hebat! - Cantik betul!

25
00:01:12,789 --> 00:01:16,700
Sila berikan tepukan untuk Prim Pariyakorn Rungruengsuk,

26
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:19,500
pengarah dan juga kekasih saya.

27
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,730
♪ Peraturan cinta, larang jatuh cinta padamu ♪

28
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:35,390
♪ Saya tahu, tapi saya tak nak dengar ♪

29
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:38,990
♪ Tapi saya lebih mahu ♪

30
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,670
♪ Hanya fikirkan awak ♪

31
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:45,560
♪ Gadis, gadis, gadis ♪

32
00:01:45,729 --> 00:01:46,860
♪ Dilarang mencintaimu ♪

33
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:49,150
♪ Gadis, gadis, gadis ♪

34
00:01:53,970 --> 00:01:59,509
♪ Gadis, gadis, gadis ♪

35
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,550
♪ Kerana saya suka gadis ♪

36
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:06,780
[Peraturan Gadis: Permainan Cinta Terlarang]

37
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:11,880
[Cuba Gadis]

38
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,180
[Cinta Plastik]

39
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:21,780
♪ Kita akan jadi lebih baik ♪

40
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:24,470
♪ Kita akan kejar impian ♪

41
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:26,800
Sekarang awak suka dengar lagu jenis apa?

42
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:31,060
Bukan ke awak kata awak tahu semua tentang saya?

43
00:02:31,170 --> 00:02:32,900
Jenis lagu pun tak boleh ingat.

44
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:36,000
Alah, manusia kan berubah mengikut masa.

45
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:39,300
Atau awak masih dengar lagu zaman sekolah menengah?

46
00:02:40,170 --> 00:02:41,100
Dengar jugalah.

47
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:42,700
Nampak tak?

48
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:44,900
Awak memang suka kenang masa lalu.

49
00:02:45,530 --> 00:02:47,870
Masih merindui masa lalu yang tak berubah.

50
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:48,930
Perkara yang sama.

51
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:50,230
Orang yang sama.

52
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,400
Semua benda awak nak kaitkan dengan diri awak, ya?

53
00:03:00,170 --> 00:03:01,770
Nak tukar disko tak?

54
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:05,900
Tak suka menari.

55
00:03:07,730 --> 00:03:09,070
Kalau metal?

56
00:03:13,330 --> 00:03:14,270
Terlalu berat.

57
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,370
Kalau lagu seksi?

58
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:31,160
Janganlah main-main, Bambi.

59
00:03:36,170 --> 00:03:45,070
Apa kata... Apa kata dengar yang ini? Gaya saya.

60
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:48,300
Aduh.

61
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:54,030
Sudahlah. Saya ikut bukan untuk diganggu oleh awak.

62
00:03:54,730 --> 00:03:56,130
Saya tak ganggu awak pun.

63
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,130
Cuma teringat masa di universiti.

64
00:03:58,530 --> 00:04:02,770
Masa itu saya tunggu awak di pasar barangan terpakai sambil pegang piring hitam.

65
00:04:02,770 --> 00:04:04,420
Masa itu awak cakap dengan saya,

66
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:06,490
awak nak dapatkan duit yang banyak

67
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,730
supaya boleh beli piring hitam tanpa fikir panjang.

68
00:04:09,970 --> 00:04:11,500
Sekarang awak dah berjaya.

69
00:04:11,770 --> 00:04:13,170
Belum sampai tahap itu lagi.

70
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:16,300
Saya kena fikir nak sara mak dan adik saya bila berbelanja.

71
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:19,500
Bukan macam awak, nak beli apa pun boleh, tak perlu kerja.

72
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:21,160
Siapa kata saya tak kerja?

73
00:04:21,529 --> 00:04:24,390
Kerjalah. Saya pun tolong mak saya uruskan jenama.

74
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:27,500
Awak tahu tak? Matlamat saya ialah

75
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,860
saya nak berjaya masuk senarai

76
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:35,930
Usahawan Wanita Paling Berpengaruh Bawah 30 Tahun di Asia.

77
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,970
Haraplah awak betul-betul boleh lakukannya.

78
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:39,900
Semuanya dah tersedia untuk awak.

79
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:42,360
Saya pasti boleh lakukannya.

80
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,730
Kalau ada teman wanita macam awak.

81
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,200
Bukan teman wanita lagi.

82
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:49,400
Saya cuma nak perhatikan tingkah laku awak dulu.

83
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,730
Jangan gembira sangat.

84
00:04:50,730 --> 00:04:52,770
Orang macam awak ni sekejap baik, sekejap jahat.

85
00:04:52,770 --> 00:04:54,300
Tak tahu bila akan berubah.

86
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:56,700
Saya cuma ada satu rupa inilah.

87
00:04:57,930 --> 00:04:58,730
Cantik.

88
00:04:59,100 --> 00:04:59,900
Kaya.

89
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:01,570
Comel.

90
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,600
Dan pandai menggoda.

91
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:08,860
Dialah orang yang awak pernah tergila-gilakan masa di universiti dulu.

92
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:11,300
"Pernah."

93
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:13,630
Cuma tergila-gilakan "dulu".

94
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,730
Sekurang-kurangnya pernah, kan?

95
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,100
Shasha.

96
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,130
Ada berus gigi tak?

97
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:30,570
Ada, di bawah.

98
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,730
Tolonglah carikan untuk saya.

99
00:05:33,730 --> 00:05:36,190
Saya tak jumpalah. Ini bukan bilik saya pun.

100
00:05:55,330 --> 00:05:56,930
Tak ada berus gigi biasa ke?

101
00:05:57,770 --> 00:05:58,570
Tak ada.

102
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:00,760
Berus gigi elektrik lagi bersih.

103
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,860
Tapi jangan risau.

104
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,200
Saya dah tukarkan kepala berus yang baru untuk awak.

105
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,660
Tak ada orang pernah guna.

106
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,070
Terima kasih.

107
00:06:09,730 --> 00:06:12,370
Tapi awak boleh anggap ini berus gigi khas untuk awak.

108
00:06:12,370 --> 00:06:14,430
Lain kali datang, guna yang ini lagi.

109
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:22,300
Saya takkan datang lagi. Lepas guna, buang saja.

110
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,770
Kita tengoklah nanti. Ini dah kali ke berapa?

111
00:06:29,770 --> 00:06:30,870
Kali ketiga, kan?

112
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:36,870
Kalau bukan sebab kawan saya tinggalkan saya semalam, saya takkan datang.

113
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:40,790
Terpulanglah awak nak jelaskan macam mana pun, asalkan awak selesa.

114
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:45,500
Tak perlu mengaku yang awak dah terpikat dengan saya.

115
00:06:46,370 --> 00:06:47,300
Macam itulah.

116
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,860
Jadi model mesti penat, kan?

117
00:07:02,530 --> 00:07:05,990
Hanya boleh makan makanan sihat, tak boleh makan benda manis.

118
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:07,650
Tak apa.

119
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:12,590
Benda manis boleh diganti dengan benda lain. Semalam saya dah makan kenyang.

120
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:15,500
Awak kena ubah perwatakan macam ni.

121
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:17,030
Ketinggalan zamanlah.

122
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,130
Habis tu, saya patut cakap macam mana?

123
00:07:19,130 --> 00:07:21,170
Saya tak tahu nak layan awak macam mana.

124
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:23,130
Awak kata nak jadi kawan tidur.

125
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,670
Tapi sekarang kita hanya "tidur".

126
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,070
Dah mula dah.

127
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:31,150
Maksud saya, kita tidur bersama itu "tidur".

128
00:07:31,590 --> 00:07:33,250
Tapi kita belum jadi "kawan".

129
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:40,530
Okey, nama saya Gorya, umur 24 tahun.

130
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,260
Keluarga saya jual makanan segera. Saya anak tunggal.

131
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:45,740
Ibu bapa nak saya belajar perubatan, tapi saya degil nak belajar fesyen.

132
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:48,340
Suka warna merah, suka muzik rock. Suka tengok filem hantu tapi takut hantu.

133
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:51,400
Hubungan paling lama setahun, putus sebab dia curang.

134
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:54,380
Tapi tak sedih lama pun. Kerja lebih penting, lagipun saya memang cantik.

135
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:58,710
Impian terbesar saya adalah untuk ada jenama pakaian sendiri bernama Gorya.

136
00:07:59,130 --> 00:08:00,330
Saya dah habis cakap.

137
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,810
Dah kenal saya, kan? Giliran awak pula.

138
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:07,300
Nama saya Shasha, 25 tahun, anak tunggal.

139
00:08:07,530 --> 00:08:10,210
Sejak umur lapan tahun, ibu hantar saya ke pertandingan dan uji bakat.

140
00:08:10,210 --> 00:08:12,960
Ada pengasuh temankan, orang paling rapat ialah pengurus saya.

141
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,900
Suka warna hitam, suka muzik klasik.

142
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,970
Hanya pernah bercinta serius sekali.

143
00:08:16,970 --> 00:08:18,890
Lepas tu baru sedar tak suka bercinta.

144
00:08:18,890 --> 00:08:20,580
Tak suka bertanggungjawab atas perasaan orang lain.

145
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:22,680
Nak buat apa, buat saja. Nak pergi mana, pergi saja.

146
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:26,880
Tak berangan tentang masa depan, yang penting gembira pada masa sekarang.

147
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:32,960
Kenapa?

148
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:45,530
Awak budak dalam iklan berus gigi tu, kan?

149
00:08:46,970 --> 00:08:48,830
Yang buat gaya ulat makan gigi tu.

150
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:49,870
Macam ni.

151
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,530
Awas ulat makan gigi, bahaya tahu.

152
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:53,700
Sudahlah tu.

153
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:55,990
Dah lama pun awak masih ingat, ya?

154
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:00,990
Nampaknya kita boleh jadi kawan.

155
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,530
Awak pun okey.

156
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,070
Kan dah cakap.

157
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,930
Sebenarnya saya comel.

158
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:10,930
Jangan fikir banyak sangat.

159
00:09:11,370 --> 00:09:14,100
Nak jadi kawan pun kena kenal satu sama lain dulu.

160
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:22,400
Saya ambilkan tisu untuk awak.

161
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:31,970
Nak beri biru?

162
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,100
Awak boleh panggil teksi dan balik.

163
00:09:42,130 --> 00:09:43,970
Saya nak pergi galeri cari Min.

164
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,470
Jomlah pergi sekali.

165
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:47,270
Kebetulan saya lapang hari ini.

166
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,970
Bukan ke awak kata ada kerja?

167
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:50,870
Pergilah tumpukan perhatian pada kerja awak.

168
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:53,000
Awak kena belajar bezakan keutamaan.

169
00:09:53,330 --> 00:09:56,870
Awak pun tahu orang macam saya ni, perasaan lebih penting daripada kerja.

170
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:57,670
Baliklah.

171
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,400
Jangan degil.

172
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,000
Bambi.

173
00:10:00,570 --> 00:10:01,900
Bila awak balik?

174
00:10:02,530 --> 00:10:05,170
Kenapa tak pergi ke acara Zee?

175
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:16,500
Maafkan saya.

176
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:18,670
Err... kita kenal ke?

177
00:10:18,930 --> 00:10:20,660
Macam mana awak tak ingat saya?

178
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,070
Saya Pae lah.

179
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:23,670
Kawan Zee.

180
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,130
Zee yang mana?

181
00:10:25,770 --> 00:10:27,070
Saya tak kenal pun.

182
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,470
Dia yang...

183
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,730
Saya rasa awak salah orang.

184
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,300
Saya tak ingat awak.

185
00:10:33,130 --> 00:10:35,200
Mungkin awak pernah nampak saya di media sosial.

186
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,600
Kalau awak peminat,

187
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:38,790
tolong beri saya ruang peribadi.

188
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,270
Helo, Bambi.

189
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,500
Bambi, alamak, Bambi.

190
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:46,870
Awak okey tak?

191
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:48,330
Kenapa awak lari?

192
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:51,270
Saya takut orang gila.

193
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:55,070
Hah?

194
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,200
Saya rasa lebih baik kita pergi hospital untuk buat pemeriksaan.

195
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,930
Macam mana kalau serius nanti?

196
00:11:00,570 --> 00:11:02,100
Tak apa, luka sikit saja ni.

197
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,100
Janganlah berlagak kuat. Nanti jadi lebih teruk.

198
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,300
Saya bawa awak pergi.

199
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,800
Jom.

200
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:13,260
[Bilik Kecemasan]

201
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:14,800
Hanya terseliuh sikit, tiada tulang yang patah.

202
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:19,200
Jangan banyak berjalan dan jangan pakai kasut tumit tinggi buat masa ini.

203
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,000
Hah?

204
00:11:20,300 --> 00:11:21,100
Tapi...

205
00:11:21,730 --> 00:11:23,870
Doktor, saya tak suka pakai stoking dengan selipar.

206
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:24,930
Aduh, Bambi.

207
00:11:25,770 --> 00:11:28,200
Kaki dah cedera pun masih fikir pasal penampilan?

208
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,170
Tak apa, doktor.

209
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:31,170
Biar saya yang uruskan selepas ini.

210
00:11:31,170 --> 00:11:31,970
Terima kasih.

211
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:42,330
Kenapa awak lari?

212
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:44,930
Kalau ada apa-apa, kenapa tak cakap?

213
00:11:45,070 --> 00:11:46,700
Saya takut orang gila.

214
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:50,100
Tapi dia tak nampak macam tu pun.

215
00:11:51,170 --> 00:11:52,900
Lagipun, dia macam kenal awak.

216
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:56,130
Mungkin dia peminat mak saya.

217
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,700
Ataupun penghendap yang nak dekat dengan saya.

218
00:12:00,730 --> 00:12:04,590
Perkara macam ni memang selalu terjadi pada orang cantik macam saya.

219
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:07,200
Janganlah bergurau.

220
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,400
Awak betul-betul tak kenal dia?

221
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:14,530
Dan orang bernama Zee yang dia sebut tu?

222
00:12:15,770 --> 00:12:16,570
Ya.

223
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,530
Saya betul-betul tak kenal.

224
00:12:18,530 --> 00:12:19,930
Tak payah pedulikan dia.

225
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:23,060
Saya masih boleh jalan tak?

226
00:12:24,530 --> 00:12:25,670
Tunggu di sini.

227
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,000
Mari.

228
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,900
Perlahan-lahan.

229
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:48,470
- Perlahan-lahan. -
- Ah.

230
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,370
Mana lagi nak cari pasangan sebaik awak, Prim?

231
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:06,930
Awak takkan jumpa.

232
00:13:07,530 --> 00:13:10,730
